Date: 1995-07-27

Title: Solvable Potentials from Supersymmetric Quantum Mechanics

Authors: Dong Sup Soh, Kyung Hyun Cho and Sang Pyo Kim

Comments: 14 pages, Latex

Journal-ref: J.Korean Phys.Soc. 28 (1995) 777-782

A recurrence relation of Riccati-type differential equations known insupersymmetric quantum mechanics is investigated to find exactly solvablepotentials. Taking some simple {\it ans\"atze}, we find new classes of solvablepotentials as well as reproducing the known shape-invariant ones.